asset.hookText: To celebrate the release of the Nike Paul Rodriguez 5, Nike SB presents Living and Learning. Chasing the next big trick is the thrill of pursuit — sometimes you win the battle, sometimes you lose. In skateboarding the war is never over. Paul knows this, and his signature product is designed to help him soldier on.
